<%- include('../partials/tw-head') -%>
<body class="flex min-h-full flex-col bg-slate-50 text-slate-800 antialiased">
<%- include('../partials/tw-header') -%>
<main class="flex-1">
  <section class="bg-navy py-14 text-white sm:py-16">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3">
        <span class="rounded-full bg-white/10 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-amber-200"><%= SITE.availability.badge %></span>
        <span class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-amber-200/80"><%= PRODUCTS.ledger.tag %></span>
      </div>
      <h1 class="mt-4 text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tight sm:text-5xl"><%= PRODUCTS.ledger.headline %></h1>
      <p class="mt-5 max-w-3xl text-lg text-slate-200 leading-relaxed"><%= PRODUCTS.ledger.subhead %></p>
      <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
        <a href="compare.html" class="inline-flex rounded-lg bg-faithGold px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-white hover:bg-amber-600 focus:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-amber-300 focus-visible:ring-offset-2 focus-visible:ring-offset-navy">Compare products</a>
        <a href="products.html" class="inline-flex rounded-lg border border-white/25 px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-white hover:bg-white/10">All products</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 py-20 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-navy">Vault first—then documents, filled exactly</h2>
    <p class="mt-4 text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">Ledger is a local-first encrypted identity vault and deterministic document prefilling system—built for sensitive data and precise execution, not as a secondary tab inside another app.</p>
    <p class="mt-4 text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">Store identity fields (including sensitive items such as a Social Security number if you choose), address and employment history, relationships, documents, and profiles for <strong class="text-navy">up to two people</strong>—for example, spouses—all encrypted on your machine.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="border-y border-slate-200 bg-white py-16">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 text-center sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-navy">People and references</h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">Track people you have known: relationship type, organization, role, relevance, and when you met.</p>
      <p class="mt-4 text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">Duration is calculated from <strong class="text-navy">local system time</strong>, so “how long you have known someone” stays accurate without manual edits.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 py-20 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-navy">Deterministic filling—never invented answers</h2>
    <p class="mt-4 text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">Ledger maps document fields to stored values and fills only exact matches. Missing data stays empty—never guessed or inferred.</p>
    <p class="mt-4 text-slate-600 leading-relaxed"><strong class="text-navy"><%= SITE.steward.name %></strong> helps parse documents, map fields, and guide workflows. It does <em>not</em> generate answers you did not provide.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-navy py-14 text-white">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 text-center sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold">Alongside CFO and Eden</h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-slate-200 leading-relaxed"><strong class="text-white">CFO</strong> handles financial operating logic. <strong class="text-white">Eden</strong> handles research ingestion and evaluation. Ledger handles identity, references, and document execution—three products, one standard, connected through <%= SITE.steward.name %>.</p>
      <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-3">
        <a href="product-cfo.html" class="rounded-lg border border-white/25 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-semibold hover:bg-white/10">CFO</a>
        <a href="product-eden.html" class="rounded-lg border border-white/25 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-semibold hover:bg-white/10">Eden</a>
        <a href="compare.html" class="rounded-lg bg-faithGold px-4 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-navy hover:bg-amber-500">Compare all</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <%- include('../partials/tw-availability') %>
</main>
<%- include('../partials/tw-footer') %>
<%- include('../partials/tw-scripts') %>
</body>
</html>
